example.code:
public bool TryGetCustomAttribute(string attributeName, out object value)
{
    if (attributeName != "CustomFloat") { value = null; return false; }
    value = this.CustomValue; return true;
}

public void SetCustomAttribute(string attributeName, object value)
{
    if (attributeName == "CustomFloat" && value is float f) this.CustomValue = f;
}

member.summary:
if meshes have Skin Weights, defines the output vertex element format:

- True: Short

- False: Float
